{"title":"python内置的函数","slug":"2019-01-24-builtfunc","date":"2019-01-24T03:12:57.000Z","updated":"2019-02-12T01:31:41.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/2019-01-24-builtfunc.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":null,"covers":null,"content":"<h4 id=\"内置的类\"><a href=\"#内置的类\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"内置的类\"></a>内置的类</h4><ul>\n<li><p><code>slice</code>，它会创建一个切片对象（是<code>slice</code>类的构造函数），可以用在任何可以进行切片操作的地方。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>对于一个切片对象实例s，可以通过s.start，s.stop，s.step来获得开始，结束，步长。</li>\n<li>可以使用<code>indices(size)</code>方法将切片映射到特定大小的序列上，防止越界。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>complex</code>，创建一个复数对象。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">complex(real,imag)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li><code>c.real</code>提取实部，<code>c.imag</code>提取虚部，<code>c.conjugate()</code>获得共轭复数</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>range</code>返回一个<code>range</code>对象，它是可迭代的</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">range(stop) </span><br><span class=\"line\">range(start,stop[,step])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>当起始值未指定，默认是0，步长默认是1</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>reversed</code>返回一个反向迭代器，只可作用于对象有确定的大小或实现了<code>__reversed__()</code>。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>enumerate</code>返回一个<code>enumerate object</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">enumerate(iterable,start=<span class=\"number\">0</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>返回(序号，元素)组成的元组，可指定序号起始值</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>zip</code>同时对多个可迭代对象进行迭代。每次返回一个元组，当有一个对象迭代完成时结束。</p>\n</li>\n<li><figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">property</span><span class=\"params\">(object)</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">   \t<span class=\"title\">property</span><span class=\"params\">(fget=None, fset=None, fdel=None, doc=None)</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"> </span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">    <span class=\"title\">Property</span> <span class=\"title\">attribute</span>.</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">      <span class=\"title\">fget</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">        <span class=\"title\">function</span> <span class=\"title\">to</span> <span class=\"title\">be</span> <span class=\"title\">used</span> <span class=\"title\">for</span> <span class=\"title\">getting</span> <span class=\"title\">an</span> <span class=\"title\">attribute</span> <span class=\"title\">value</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">      <span class=\"title\">fset</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">        <span class=\"title\">function</span> <span class=\"title\">to</span> <span class=\"title\">be</span> <span class=\"title\">used</span> <span class=\"title\">for</span> <span class=\"title\">setting</span> <span class=\"title\">an</span> <span class=\"title\">attribute</span> <span class=\"title\">value</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">      <span class=\"title\">fdel</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">        <span class=\"title\">function</span> <span class=\"title\">to</span> <span class=\"title\">be</span> <span class=\"title\">used</span> <span class=\"title\">for</span> <span class=\"title\">del</span>'<span class=\"title\">ing</span> <span class=\"title\">an</span> <span class=\"title\">attribute</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">      <span class=\"title\">doc</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">        <span class=\"title\">docstring</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">    <span class=\"title\">Typical</span> <span class=\"title\">use</span> <span class=\"title\">is</span> <span class=\"title\">to</span> <span class=\"title\">define</span> <span class=\"title\">a</span> <span class=\"title\">managed</span> <span class=\"title\">attribute</span> <span class=\"title\">x</span>:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">C</span><span class=\"params\">(object)</span>:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"title\">getx</span><span class=\"params\">(self)</span>:</span> <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> self._x</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"title\">setx</span><span class=\"params\">(self, value)</span>:</span> self._x = value</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"title\">delx</span><span class=\"params\">(self)</span>:</span> <span class=\"keyword\">del</span> self._x</span><br><span class=\"line\">        x = property(getx, setx, delx, <span class=\"string\">\"I'm the 'x' property.\"</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    Decorators make defining new properties <span class=\"keyword\">or</span> modifying existing ones easy:</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">C</span><span class=\"params\">(object)</span>:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">        @property</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"title\">x</span><span class=\"params\">(self)</span>:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"string\">\"I am the 'x' property.\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> self._x</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">        @x.setter</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"title\">x</span><span class=\"params\">(self, value)</span>:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            self._x = value</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">        @x.deleter</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"title\">x</span><span class=\"params\">(self)</span>:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">del</span> self._x</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">super</span><span class=\"params\">(object)</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">   \t<span class=\"title\">super</span><span class=\"params\">()</span> -&gt; same as super(__class__, &lt;first argument&gt;)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">    super(type) -&gt; unbound super object</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">    super(type, obj) -&gt; bound super object; requires isinstance(obj, type)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">    super(type, type2) -&gt; bound super object; requires issubclass(type2, type)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">    </span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\">    Typical use to call a cooperative superclass method:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        </span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">C</span><span class=\"params\">(B)</span>:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"title\">meth</span><span class=\"params\">(self, arg)</span>:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            super().meth(arg)</span><br><span class=\"line\">            </span><br><span class=\"line\">    This works <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">methods</span> <span class=\"title\">too</span>:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        </span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">C</span><span class=\"params\">(B)</span>:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">        @classmethod</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"title\">cmeth</span><span class=\"params\">(cls, arg)</span>:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            super().cmeth(arg)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li></li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"内置函数\"><a href=\"#内置函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"内置函数\"></a>内置函数</h4><ul>\n<li><p><code>min</code>，返回最小值，可以传入可调用对象指定比较关键字</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">min(iterable,*[, default=obj, key=func])</span><br><span class=\"line\">min(arg1, arg2, *args, *[,key=func])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>max</code>与<code>min</code>类似</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>sum</code>返回从起始值累加的结果</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sum(iterable, start=<span class=\"number\">0</span>, /)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>any</code>如果有可迭代对象中元素x使得<code>bool(x)</code>为真，则返回真。若对象为空，返回假</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">any(iterable,/)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>format</code>格式化输出，指定宽度和精度的一般格式为<code>[&lt;&gt;^]?width[,]?(.digits)?</code>，同样适用于字符串的<code>.format</code>方法</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">format(value,format_sepc=<span class=\"string\">''</span>,/)</span><br><span class=\"line\">format(<span class=\"number\">1234.56789</span>,<span class=\"string\">'^10.1f'</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>round</code>取整函数，用于将数字取整到固定小数位。当某个值恰好等于两个整数间的一半时，取整会取到离该值最接近的偶数上。当传递的<code>ndigits</code>为负数时，会相应的取整到十位，百位</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">round(number,ndigits=<span class=\"keyword\">None</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>bin</code>，<code>oct</code>，<code>hex</code>会把整数转换为二进制，八进制，十六进制文本字符串形式。当不想出现相应的进制前缀时，可以使用<code>format(x,&#39;o&#39;)</code>函数。将其他进制数转换为十进制数可使用<code>int(x,base=10)</code>并指明数值的进制。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>len</code>返回一个可迭代对象中元素的数量</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">len(obj,/)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>next</code>返回迭代器的下一个元素</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">next(iterator[,default])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>如果指定<code>default</code>则遇到迭代结束返回给定值代替<code>StopIteration</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>iter</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">iter(iterable) <span class=\"comment\">#调用可迭代对象的__iter()__方法，返回一个迭代器</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">iter(callable,sentinel) <span class=\"comment\">#接受一个无参的可调用对象和一个哨兵作为输入；创建一个迭代器重复调用可调用对象直到返回哨兵时停止</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>isinstance</code>检查一个对象是否是一个类的实例或它的子类</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">isinstance(obj,class_or_tuple,/)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>当给定一个元组时，会依次对元组中的元素进行检查。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>open</code>函数用于打开文件，返回一个文件对象。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">open(file,mode=<span class=\"string\">'r'</span>,buffering=<span class=\"number\">-1</span>,encoding=<span class=\"keyword\">None</span>,errors=<span class=\"keyword\">None</span>,newline=<span class=\"keyword\">None</span>,closefd=<span class=\"keyword\">True</span>,opener=<span class=\"keyword\">None</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>print</code>输出数据</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">print(value,...,sep=<span class=\"string\">' '</span>,end=<span class=\"string\">'\\n'</span>,file=sys.stdout,flush=<span class=\"keyword\">False</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>数据默认输出到标准输出也就是屏幕，当需要将输出重定向到文件中，只需要指定<code>file</code>关键字参数，文件要以文本模式打开</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n","categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"python","slug":"python","count":7,"path":"api/tags/python.json"}]}